OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774015869
OL,3,CRapist who threatened woman has
OL,4,Csentence increased
OL,6,FA man convicted of raping a woman and
OL,7,Flater attempting to pressure her into
OL,8,Fdropping the case has had his prison
OL,9,Fsentence increased following
OL,10,Fintervention by the Solicitor
OL,11,FGeneral's Office.
OL,13,FIonut Tanae, 33, from Nelson in
OL,14,FLancashire, had his sentence extended
OL,15,Fby three years and seven months after
OL,16,Fthe case was referred to the Court of
OL,17,FAppeal under the Unduly Lenient
OL,18,FSentence scheme.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
