PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774015869
OL,3,CRapist who threatened woman has
OL,4,Csentence increased
OL,6,FThe court heard that Tanae raped the
OL,7,Fvictim on two separate occasions,
OL,8,Fbefore later breaking into her home
OL,9,Fand attempting to persuade her to
OL,10,Fwithdraw her complaint.
OL,12,FAfter being charged and remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody, he then wrote to the victim
OL,14,Fand again tried to convince her to
OL,15,Fdrop the case.
OL,17,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,18,Fwoman described suffering from
OL,19,Fdepression and anxiety, as well as
OL,20,Foverwhelming feelings of shame.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774015869
OL,3,CRapist who threatened woman has
OL,4,Csentence increased
OL,6,FThe Solicitor General Ellie Reeves KC
OL,7,FMP said the crimes had a "devastating"
OL,8,Fimpact.
OL,10,FShe added that Tanae had not only
OL,11,Fraped the victim more than once, but
OL,12,Fhad also continued a campaign of
OL,13,Fintimidation, even while in custody.
OL,15,FShe said the original sentence did not
OL,16,Freflect the full seriousness of the
OL,17,Foffences and welcomed the decision to
OL,18,Fincrease it, praising the victim's
OL,19,Fbravery.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
