PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774015869
OL,3,CRapist who threatened woman has
OL,4,Csentence increased
OL,6,F"No one should have to endure what the
OL,7,Fvictim went through, and the original
OL,8,Fsentence did not reflect the true
OL,9,Fgravity of his offending," she said.
OL,11,FTanae was originally sentenced at
OL,12,FPreston Crown Court on 26 November
OL,13,F2025 to eight years and six months in
OL,14,Fprison after being convicted of two
OL,15,Fcounts of rape, two counts of
OL,16,Fperverting the course of justice and
OL,17,Fone count of burglary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
