PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774015869
OL,3,CRapist who threatened woman has
OL,4,Csentence increased
OL,6,FFollowing the referral, judges at the
OL,7,FCourt of Appeal increased his sentence
OL,8,Fto 12 years and one month on 19 March
OL,9,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
